iv></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="neos-nodetypes-text nodetypes-content"><div><p><i><strong>All rates are subject to change.</strong></i></p></div></section></div></div><section class="neos-nodetypes-text nodetypes-content"><div><p>Thanks to your entrance ticket, you have access to the festival area and can see the balloons taking off just a few meters away from you!</p><p><strong>The Festival ticket also includes:</strong></p><ul><li>reduction of CHF 5.- for tickets for the new Espace Ballon exhibition (at CHF 13.- instead of CHF 18.-)</li><li>the viewing of the film on the L'Etivaz AOP cheese making process at the Caves de L'Etivaz and</li><li>the philatelic exhibition</li></ul></div></section></div></div></div></div><div class="tc-website-rootcontainer nodetypes-content background-white "><div class="container"><div class="content"><div class="neos-contentcollection" data-children-count="2"><div class="tc-neos-elements-space nodetypes-content" style="height:50px"></div><div class="right-overlap-container mb-5"><div class="right-overlap-image"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/25d0dcca7823e99d6c7e56b751ed9a87b6fe29ad/IMG_8694.jpg" width="2085" height="2085" /></div><div class="right-overlap-content"><div class="neos-contentcollection" data-children-count="2"><div class="neos-nodetypes-headline nodetypes-content"><div><h2>Festival pins 2024</h2></div></div><section class="neos-nodetypes-text nodetypes-content"><div><p><strong>The festival pin gives you access </strong>to the event during the 9 days! It also allows you to visit <a href="/en/programme/activites">the philatelic exhibition</a>, to watch <a href="/en/programme/activites">the Caves de l'Etivaz film</a> for free and get a discount on <a href="/en/programme/activites">the new Espace Ballon exhibition</a>.</p><p><strong>The 2024 pin</strong> is on sale at the Château-d'Œx tourist office!</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></section></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="tc-website-rootcontainer nodetypes-content background-white "><div class="container"><div class="content"><div class="neos-contentcollection" data-children-count="5"><div class="tc-neos-elements-space nodetypes-content" style></div><div class="neos-nodetypes-headline nodetypes-content"><div><h1>access</h1></div></div><section class="neos-nodetypes-text nodetypes-content"><div><h3>Take the public transports to reach the International Balloon Festival!</h3><p>Forget the stress of traffic jams and take public transport to the festival!</p></div></section><section class="tc-neos-elements-bootstrap-accordion nodetypes-content panel-group accordion" id="accordion-885cf041-4471-488b-a503-ba9b4be11ea3" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true"><section class="tc-neos-elements-bootstrap-accordionitem nodetypes-content panel tc-neos-elements-bootstrap-accordionitem"><section class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading-item-44b1e8c7-13fc-49fc-a6aa-1e310b0206d2"><h4 class="panel-title"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#item-44b1e8c7-13fc-49fc-a6aa-1e310b0206d2" aria-expanded="true"><sup>BY TRAIN</sup></a></h4></section><section id="item-44b1e8c7-13fc-49fc-a6aa-1e310b0206d2" role="tabpanel" class="panel-collapse collapse in show" data-parent="#accordion-885cf041-4471-488b-a503-ba9b4be11ea3" aria-labelledby="heading-item-44b1e8c7-13fc-49fc-a6aa-1e310b0206d2" aria-expanded="true"><section class="panel-body"><section class="neos-nodetypes-text nodetypes-content"><div><h3>From Montreux, Zweisimmen and Interlaken</h3></div></section><div class="columns-25-75 neos-nodetypes-columnlayouts-twocolumn nodetypes-content neos-nodetypes-multicolumn"><div class="column column-25 neos-contentcollection" data-children-count="1"><div class="neos-nodetypes-image nodetypes-content"><figure class="neos-alignment-center"><a target="_blank" href="https://journey.mob.ch/en/"><picture><source srcset="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/276b3d340fc7d9ce4ac75acb591cd73817e3b514/mob.jpg" media="(max-width: 479px)" /><source srcset="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/276b3d340fc7d9ce4ac75acb591cd73817e3b514/mob.jpg" media="(max-width: 767px)" /><source srcset="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/cb37390aa7bd302f1f63d7d46dedfbf46912a7b2/mob-300x150.jpg" media="(max-width: 991px)" /><source srcset="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/276b3d340fc7d9ce4ac75acb591cd73817e3b514/mob.jpg" media="(max-width: 1199px)" /><source srcset="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/276b3d340fc7d9ce4ac75acb591cd73817e3b514/mob.jpg" media="(min-width: 1200px)" /><source srcset="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/f4e22fc5a284eaf94972c58439a9fce929ae4f96/mob-1x1.jpg" media="(min-width: 1400px)" /><img loading="lazy" alt="Compagnie du Chemin de fer Montreux Oberland bernois" src="https://www.festivaldeballons.ch/_Resources/Persistent/f4e22fc5a284eaf94972c58439a9fce929ae4f96/mob-1x1.jpg" style="max-width:120px" title="MOB" /></picture></a></figure></div></div><div class="column column-75 neos-contentcollection" data-children-count="2"><section class="neos-nodetypes-text nodetypes-content"><div><p><strong>via the GoldenPass train line / Compagnie du Chemin de fer Montreux Oberland bernois</strong></p><p><strong>The MOB </strong>serves Château-d'Œx with one train running each hour. With their panoramic trains, the adventure begins from the moment you leave the first station. As soon as you arrive in the Pays-d'Enhaut region, discover the first hot-air balloons, from your seat, through the large windows!</p><p>All the information you need about ticket prices<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://journey.mob.ch/en/stories/festival-international-des-ballons-a-chateau-doex"> is available here!</a></p></div></section><div class="tc-neos-elements-button nodetypes-content left "><div class="btn-position"><button class="btn button